thread.title_full: Lucky Tackle Box reviewed by Daryl M. Stump

author: Daryl M. Stump
title: Daryl M. Stump
text: I had a status and question about my subscription. The response was quick and extremely helpful. Nichole provided first class assistance in regards to my subscription. My son is very pleased with the items he is receiving in his Lucky Tackle Box and based on my positive experience I would not hesitate to recommend Lucky Tackle Box to anyone. Thank you Nichole and LTB Support.
